data.description: Welcome home to this charming property with a natural color palette that exudes warmth throughout. The kitchen boasts a nice backsplash, perfect for any chef. The master bedroom features a walk-in closet for ample storage. Other rooms offer flexible living space to fit your needs. The primary bathroom includes good under sink storage. Step outside to a fenced backyard with a sitting area, ideal for relaxing. With fresh interior and exterior paint, this home feels brand new. Partial flooring replacement in some areas adds a modern touch. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this house your home!
